    dc:description "Fig. 1. Phylogenetic tree (maximum likelihood) of Andrena subgenus Aciandrena Warncke, 1968 based on the mitochondrial COI gene. Numbers adjacent to branches represent bootstrap support (values of <75 are omitted). Species belonging to the subgenus Graecandrena Warncke, 1968 are marked in different shades of blue, and species belonging to the subgenus Parandrenella Popov, 1958 are marked in grey." ;
